cs.CV, cs.MM, cs.IT, cs.LG, cs.DS

This paper deals with image processing techniques for removing noise from colour images while preserving edges and fine details. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). Other likely sub-categories include cs.MM (Multimedia), cs.IT (Information Theory), cs.LG (Machine Learning), and cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms), as these fields are also relevant to the study of image processing and filtering techniques.
